features: COMFORTABLE AND BREATHABLE: Rainberg working gloves are Seamless knit shell offers Good Comfort, finger Dexterity and Breathability. The strength of these work gloves is significantly better than the regular cotton gloves.

MULTIPLE USES: Ideal for general light to medium duty tasks in dry and slightly wet/oily conditions, such as general purpose, DIY, Assembly, Auto Repairing, Warehouse, Construction, Home improvement, Yard, Gardening, Cleaning. Not Recommended for heavy duty work and any heavy oily/wet conditions.
Non-SLIP: With Polyurethane coated palm and fingertips, Rainberg safety work gloves provides a secure grip in dry and slightly wet/oily conditions and offers high dexterity and tactile sensitivity.
CAUTION: Recommend washing gloves in tempered water not exceeding 104℉ or 40℃. A mild non-ionic laundry soap or detergent should be used. Wash in a 5–10-minute cycle time. Rinse in cold water.
